Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE and Blue Commercial have pleasure in offering for sale Suite 2, Eastside, 232 Robina Town Centre Drive, Robina.

This high yielding investment is underpinned by a secure long term lease to City Fertility Clinic who have occupied since June 2009.

Eastside is located within CBD Robina, a recognised Principal Activity Centre under State Government and Gold Coast City Council Regional Economic Plans which is supported by a range of large infrastructure including Robina Public & Private Hospitals, Robina Train Station & Transit Hub, CBUS Super Stadium, Robina Town Centre.  It is a fully occupied four level strata titled office building comprising of 33 strata lots with basement + on-grade parking and an onsite café.  


INVESTMENT HIGHLIGHTS

- Medical tenant – long term occupier
- Lease expiry in late 2024
- Net income $99,656* pa
- 199sqm*
- Ground level shopfront with exposure to Robina Town Centre Drive
- 10 carparks+
- Light box panel above shopfront
- Zone: Special Purpose under Robina Central Planning Agreement
- Medical use approval
- Strategically positioned investment in close proximity to Robina Town Centre, Robina Hospital & Robina Transit Hub.

*approx
+subject to CMS amendment

The Easy T Centre is designed for a busy lifestyle that demands convenience, freshness and choice without compromising on style. Its fresh open design will do much to create a welcoming environment and provide a positive shopping experience; along with over 290 on-grade car parks, excellent accessibility & traffic exposure to over thousands of vehicles per day.

Anchored by Aldi Supermarket, Easy-T provides over 35 specialty retailers with a strong mix of local & national tenants including Nightowl Convenience, Zarraffa's, Amcal Pharmacy, Mrs Flannery's Grocer, Tattsbet, Brumbys Bakery, Taboon Restaurant, TukTuk Thai Restaurant, Subway and Krish Indian Restaurant just to name a few.
